GR-Based IV:-
		
	GR-Based IV stands for Goods Receipt-Based Invoice Verification.

     It is a feature in SAP MM where the vendor invoice is verified against the Goods Receipt (GR) instead of only against the Purchase Order (PO).

     This ensures that the vendor is paid only for the quantity of goods that has actually been received.		


